title: Test
summary: This grouped bar chart has 3 categories of Country on the x axis representing 2 groups: Males, and Females.
Averaging these 2 groups, the highest category is found for Country Canada with a mean value of 82.0.
Followed by USA with a mean value of 78.5.
The lowest category is observed at North America that has a mean value of 78.5
showing a difference of 4.4% with the maximum value.
In case of Canada, Males shows more dominance than any other Country and it has the lowest value in North America.
